# File Map

## Hooks
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/hooks/useLivekitRoom.js` | LiveKit Room connect/disconnect with exponential backoff reconnection. Locally-scoped cancellation for Strict Mode safety. |
| `src/hooks/useSignalingSocket.js` | Socket.IO client connection. Emits joinStage/leaveStage. Sets `window.socket`. |
| `src/hooks/useUserMedia.js` | `getUserMedia` wrapper: camera/mic selection, device enumeration, toggling, error state. |
| `src/hooks/useStageInfo.js` | Loads stage + features from Supabase. Realtime subscription for live updates. CRUD helpers for features. |

## Context Providers
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/components/RealtimeContext.js` | Multi-stream broadcast state, LiveKit room, Socket.IO socket, peer streams, stream selection, simulcast quality control. |
| `src/components/UserMediaContext.js` | Wraps `useUserMedia`, provides local stream + device info. |
| `src/components/StageContext.js` | Wraps `useStageInfo`, provides stage data + feature CRUD to children. |
| `src/components/EditorContext.js` | Determines isEditor from Supabase auth + collaborator_ids. |

## Broadcaster
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/components/BroadcastStreamControls/index.js` | Stream sink selector, occupancy detection, publish/unpublish with 3Mbps VP8 simulcast. |

## Audience
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/components/Stage/index.js` | Main stage: broadcast video + interactive sketches + StreamSwitcher overlay. |
| `src/components/VideoObject.js` | `BroadcastVideoSurface` (video element) + `BroadcastAudioPlayer` (audio element) with tab-visibility fix. |

## Stage Manager
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/components/Editor/FeaturesList/index.js` | Feature list: add/remove/reorder sketches and broadcast streams. |
| `src/components/Editor/FlexPanel/index.js` | Stage actions: show state transitions, audience controls, lobby toggle. |

## Server
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `server/index.js` | Express + Socket.IO. Relay, peerInfo, emotes, audience counts. Room-scoped messaging. |
| `src/app/api/livekit/token/route.js` | LiveKit token generation with Supabase auth validation. |

## Config
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `src/config.js` | Feature flags (`LOBBY_ENABLED`). |
| `shared/defaultDBEntries.js` | Factory functions for default stage, feature, and broadcastStream records. |
